---
// Chapter 02: The Origin — About
---

<section class="about chapter-section" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-layout">
      <div class="about-left">
        <span class="chapter-num reveal reveal-scale">CH.02</span>
        <h2 class="section-heading reveal reveal-up delay-1">
          The <em class="serif">Origin</em> Story
        </h2>
        <p class="about-body reveal reveal-up delay-2">
          My work spans <strong>enterprise travel platforms</strong>, institutional finance automation, and AI-powered tools — environments where usability must coexist with operational logic.
        </p>
        <div class="about-quote reveal reveal-left delay-3" data-parallax="-0.08">
          <div class="quote-mark">❝</div>
          <p>I don't start with screens.<br/><strong>I start with structure.</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-right">
        <div class="question-block reveal reveal-right delay-2" data-depth="1.2">
          <div class="qb-header">
            <span class="qb-tag">BEFORE I DESIGN, I ASK —</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="qb-list">
            <li class="reveal reveal-up delay-2">
              <span class="qb-num">01</span>
              <span>Who is making the decision?</span>
            </li>
            <li class="reveal reveal-up delay-3">
              <span class="qb-num">02</span>
              <span>What are they trying to complete?</span>
            </li>
            <li class="reveal reveal-up delay-4">
              <span class="qb-num">03</span>
              <span>Where does friction exist?</span>
            </li>
            <li class="reveal reveal-up delay-5">
              <span class="qb-num">04</span>
              <span>What constraints must be respected?</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="qb-footer">
            <p>Strong UX isn't decoration.</p>
            <p><strong>It's structured problem-solving.</strong></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-body {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--dark-grey);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .about-body strong { color: var(--black); }

  .about-quote {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 20px;
    border: var(--border-thick);
    background: var(--neon-yellow);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    transform: rotate(-1deg);
  }

  .quote-mark {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .about-quote p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .about-quote strong { font-weight: 900; }

  /* Question block */
  .question-block {
    border: var(--border-brutal);
    background: var(--white);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  .qb-header {
    padding: 16px 24px;
    border-bottom: var(--border-thick);
    background: var(--black);
  }

  .qb-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--neon-green);
  }

  .qb-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .qb-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 16px 24px;
    border-bottom: var(--border-thin);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    transition: background 0.15s ease;
  }

  .qb-list li:hover {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding-left: 32px;
  }

  .qb-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .qb-num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--neon-pink);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 28px;
  }

  .qb-footer {
    padding: 16px 24px;
    border-top: var(--border-thick);
    background: var(--cream);
  }

  .qb-footer p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--dark-grey);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .qb-footer strong { color: var(--black); }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .about-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    .about-quote { transform: rotate(0deg); }
  }
</style>
